Package: PrinciplesSTA
Title: Principles of Spatial Transcriptomics Analysis with Bioconductor
Description: This package contains source code and materials for the 
    'Principles of Spatial Transcriptomics Analysis with Bioconductor' online 
    book. The book contains examples of analysis steps and workflows 
    demonstrating principles of spatial transcriptomics analyses using the 
    Bioconductor framework in R. The examples include R code and downloadable 
    datasets.
Version: 0.99.0
